Description:

The task is to create a program about the number PI, given that 'PImavera' has arrived.
Specifically, we need a program that, each time a key is pressed, displays one more digit of the number PI. Starting with 3.14, then 3.141, and so on successively.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Program:

To try this program, just run: "php YourFileDirectory/PiNumber.php" on the terminal and voilà! To quit the program, just press ctrl + c on the terminal.
PS!! I could only make -press enter- to work and not any keys :c

